(3, 3, 'HUAWEI Nova 2i with Free Color Band A2', '<h3>Brand-New Experience From Every Detail</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The HUAWEI Y7 mobile phone adopts a bold new design and craft based on its 5.5-inch display. The rondure of the front 2.5D glass perfectly links the screen with the body, giving the impression of a floating display when you turn on the screen. The HUAWEI Y7 smartphone&rsquo;s metal body combines both durability and lightness, giving you an uncompromising touch experience. The whole rondure design, sandblasted surface, and embossed camera edge are as brilliant to look at as it is to touch.</span></p>\r\n', '<div class=\"box-collateral-content\">\r\n<div class=\"std\">\r\n<h2>Huawei Y7 2GB/16GB Smartphone</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Operating System: Android 7.0 (Nougat) + +EMUI5.1</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Processor: Octa-core 1.4 GHz Cortex-A53</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8940 Snapdragon 435</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Display Size: 5.5 inches, IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Display Resolution: 720 x 1280 pixels, 16:9 ratio</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">RAM: 2GB</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">ROM: 16GB</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Rear Camera: 12 MP phase detection autofocus, LED flash</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Front Camera: 8 MP, f/2.0</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Sensors: Proximity sensor, Ambient light sensor, Compass, Gravity sensor, Phone status indicator</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Battery Size: Non-removable Li-Ion 4000 mAh battery</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Huawei Y7 in Bangladesh\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/Huawei-Y7.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Huawei Y7\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Brand-New Experience From Every Detail</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The HUAWEI Y7 mobile phone adopts a bold new design and craft based on its 5.5-inch display. The rondure of the front 2.5D glass perfectly links the screen with the body, giving the impression of a floating display when you turn on the screen. The HUAWEI Y7 smartphone&rsquo;s metal body combines both durability and lightness, giving you an uncompromising touch experience. The whole rondure design, sandblasted surface, and embossed camera edge are as brilliant to look at as it is to touch.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Buy Huawei Y7\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/Huawei-Y7-Display.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Huawei Y7\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4000mAh Battery, Maximum Endurance</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">With the HUAWEI Y7 mobile phone&rsquo;s 4000mAh (typical value) high-density battery, you can enjoy your phone for longer. As the capacity retention rate is greater than 80% even after 500 times of recharge cycles, you don&rsquo;t have to worry about replacing the battery over the device&rsquo;s lifetime. The HUAWEI&rsquo;s own power saving technology offers you smooth user experience when watching videos (20 hours) or browsing (15 hours).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Huawei Y7 mobile battery\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/Huawei-Y7-Battery.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Huawei Y7 Battery\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Easier To Take Better-Looking Photos</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The 12MP rear camera on the HUAWEI Y7 carries a larger 1.25 &mu;m pixel sensor, which adds more light-sensing surface area, and lets you take great quality photos even under low light conditions. Phase Detection Auto Focus (PDAF) allows you to focus on your subject in just 0.3s*, making sure you capture all of life&rsquo;s spontaneous moments with clear and sharp details. The 8MP front camera features face recognition technology and beauty mode, which helps remove blemishes and improves brightness. Keep every moment perfect with the HUAWEI Y7 smartphone.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Huawei Y7 Camera\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/Huawei-Y7-Camera.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Huawei Y7 Camera\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Speed Up Your Life</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The HUAWEI Y7 mobile&rsquo;s speedy Octa-core CPU is equipped with 8 Cortex-A53 processors, hitting speeds of up to 1.4GHz, 2GB* of RAM allows you run more apps at once to offer you a way to enjoy all your entertainment needs. With 16GB of storage expandable by another 128GB MicroSD card**, you have the freedom to save your favorite music and apps.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>EMUI5.1, A Fresh New Experience</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">EMUI 5.1 provides an in-depth customization and refreshing new interpretation of Android 7.0. With a brand new redesigned interface, over 90% of core operations can be completed in just 3 steps. And new features like Eye Comfort Mode helps you filter out blue light and provides relief to visual fatigue.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '26000', '25000', 0, 'Huawei', 'upload/cfc2570e71.jpg', 0, '2018-03-30 18:00:00'),
(4, 4, 'Nokia 1', '<p>Want it by Tomorrow, <strong>31 March..?</strong> Order within <strong>13 hrs 5 mins </strong> and get your order delivery by tomorrow 8PM, by choosing <strong>FastPick</strong> at checkout.</p>\r\n', '<div class=\"box-collateral-content\">\r\n<div class=\"std\">\r\n<h2>Nokia 1 Smartphone</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Nokia 1 in Bangladesh\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/nokia-1-cover.png\" style=\"float:right; height:363px; width:265px\" title=\"Nokia 1\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Operating System: Android 8.1 Oreo (Go edition)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Processor: MT6737M Quad Core 1.1 GHz</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Display Size &amp; Type: 4.5&rdquo; FWVGA IPS display</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">RAM: 1 GB LPDDR3 RAM</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">ROM: 8 GB eMMC</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">SIM: Dual Nano SIM</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Rear camera: 5 MP rear camera with LED flash</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Front Camera: 2 MP front camera</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Battery: Removable 2150 mAh battery</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:small\">Sensors: Proximity, Ambient light, G-sensor</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The <strong>Nokia 1&nbsp;</strong>has been introducing itself as Set up to Smarter. Its inherent coloring will persuade you to hide your life&#39;s knock. The first smartphone in Nokia which comes with Android Go operating system.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nokia 1 Mobile Phone: Android Go (All the apps you need)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Nokia 1 comes with Android 8.1 Oreo (Go edition), optimized so you can use apps faster, without annoying lags. Plus, the pre-loaded apps are designed to use less storage space and data, so you&rsquo;ll be able to do more and fit more photos and apps on your phone.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Nokia 1 doesn&rsquo;t hold back. A powerful experience in our most affordable package, with all your favourite apps like WhatsApp, Facebook, YouTube, Google Maps and many more, literally at your fingertips. You won&rsquo;t miss a beat.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Nokia 1 comes with Google Assistant Go edition. Ask questions, tell it to do things, whatever you like &ndash; just say the word.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Android 8.1. Oreo (Go edition) has no unnecessary apps or hidden processes eating up your battery life and phone memory.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Worry less about wasting data with the Chrome Data Saver. You&rsquo;ll save up to 60% of mobile data.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Watch now, and Later</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Nokia 1 comes with YouTube Go, designed to run faster and use less data while you view videos and stream. You can choose the playback quality and even download videos to watch offline later.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Android go with Nokia 1\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/nokia-1-android-go_1.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Nokia 1\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\">Nokia 1 Cell Phone: Processor; SIM; Network (Get More Done)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Smooth to use, Nokia 1 is full of possibilities. Enjoy 4G LTE connectivity for streaming and surfing, and easily switch between SIM cards thanks to Dual SIM. Or take advantage of the MicroSD storage card slot to expand storage up to 128 GB.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Specification of Nokia 1\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/nokia-1-storage.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Nokia 1\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nokia 1 Mobile: Design (Your next Phone)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Nokia 1 offers an optimized smartphone experience, accessible to everyone. Its design details give it the iconic look you love and the durability you need. And the exchangeable Xpress-on covers are back too. Some things are timeless.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nokia 1 Smartphone: Camera (Cherish the Moment)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Relive those special moments and stay connected. Capture the world around you with the 5 MP rear camera with LED flash or share selfies and make video calls with the 2 MP front camera.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><img alt=\"Nokia 1 Cherish the Moment\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/nokia-1-camera.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" title=\"Nokia 1\" /></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '75000', '0', 0, 'Nokia', 'upload/85419ab2ec.jpg', 2, '2018-04-24 18:00:00'),
