r group selfies. Front camera of Mi Max 2 is able to record 720p videos.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Snapdragon 625 Chipset Use in Xiaomi Mi Max 2\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/mi-max-2-performance.jpg\" style=\"float:left; height:217px; width:505px\" title=\"Xiaomi Mi Max 2\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Xiaomi Mi Max 2 Cell Phone: Hardware; Memory; Battery</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2.0 GHz Octa-Core processor has used in this Xiaomi cell phone device. 4GB RAM with the 2.0GHZ Octa-Core processor and Snapdragon 625 Chipset will give you an incredible smartphone device for gaming, watching videos, reading books and browsing, without any interruption. 64GB gigantic storage is able to store your valuable files. 5300mAh non-removable Li-ion battery will give full day operating with out any power loss. It has quick charging+prallal charging technology.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Split Screen has Xiaomi Mi Max 2\" src=\"https://d1lwfjp709sq0o.cloudfront.net/media/wysiwyg/sz/xiaomi-mi-max-2-split-screen_1.jpg\" style=\"float:left; height:289px; width:369px\" title=\"Xiaomi Mi Max 2\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Split screen mode</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">One screen, two different types of content. &nbsp;Watch a video while chatting. Compare products or take notes while reading. Check a map while getting directions from a friend. &nbsp;No need to constantly switch between two apps.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '28990', '24990', 0, 'Xiaomi', 'upload/999802c95c.jpg', 3, '2018-04-21 18:00:00'),
